c: 35
v: 8
t: "Ngakube lowo owenzelwe izenzo zakhe ezimbi zabukeka zizinhle uzibona zizinhle ngakho-ke ngempela uMvelinqangi udukisa lowo amthandayo, futhi uholela (endleleni eqondile) lowo amthandayo, ngakho-ke awungaphatheki kabi umphefumulo wakho ngabo, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyisazi ngalokho abakwenzayo"